title: Alex Vaz, Henry Menezes to conduct football seminar
text:
Alex Vaz, Henry Menezes to conduct football seminar By A Correspondent | Posted 1 hour 
Former FIFA referee Alex Vaz and WIFA CEO Henry Menezes will be the principle speakers at a seminar Focus on FIFA Laws of the Game on October 16 at Divine Child Pre Primary School, near Amboli in Andheri. 
Vaz, one of Indiaâ€™s most distinguished referees, will explain football rules and changing laws, while Menezes will provide players perspective. The seminar is free for referees, coaches and club owners. For details contact Alex Vaz (9869412588), Everest Gonsalves (9820168091). Tags:
